## Limitations

The research is limited by the availability of translated texts and the potential bias in historical interpretations. Many original manuscripts remain untranslated, which may contain additional insights into the development of astronomy in the Arab world. Furthermore, the reliance on secondary sources may introduce interpretative biases that could affect the conclusions drawn.